{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/lvl2_new_crop.gif?t=1722425671\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\ud83d\ude80<strong> UNIQUE BOOMERANG MECHANIC!</strong> Think outside the box to both move your character and aim and throw your boomerang at the same time to interact with the game's varied mechanics. You've never played a platformer quite like this.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\ud83c\udf0c<strong> Enjoy a sci-fi story about disability told from a person who's seen it first hand.</strong> Never interrupting gameplay, but provoking deep thoughts in-between levels.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/lvl7_new_crop.gif?t=1722425671\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\ud83e\udde0<strong> Chase times on online leaderboards</strong> with Sophia's intuitive, multi-layered, and skill expressive moveset!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\ud83c\udf6a<strong> Collect cookies and cosmetics. Discover secrets.</strong> More than 100 tasty collectables are waiting. Use them to upgrade your fashion. But they are not the only secrets on this planet...</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/lvl5_new_crop.gif?t=1722425671\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\ud83c\udfc3\u200d\u2640\ufe0f<strong> Fight bosses, run for your life.</strong> The end of (almost) every level holds a challenge. 3 Bosses to defeat and a lot of deadly traps to avoid.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/story_new_crop.gif?t=1722425671\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/variery_gif_crop.gif?t=1722425671\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Just getting start